    <item>
      <title>制裁限制出口后，俄罗斯北极液化天然气二号项目几乎无法产出天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/russia-s-arctic-lng-2-barely-pumps-any-gas-after-sanctions-lock-in-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于西方国家的制裁，俄罗斯的北极液化天然气二号项目上个月停止了液化作业，截至 11 月份，该项目已将其天然气田的产量削减至几乎为零。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/russia-s-arctic-lng-2-barely-pumps-any-gas-after-sanctions-lock-in-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 07:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
